data.description: Welcome to your move-in ready oasis in the heart of West Knoxville! This updated home, conveniently located near freeways, offers the perfect blend of convenience and comfort.Ideal for first time homebuyers and young couples. Equipped with a large bonus room and separate lower-level entrance providing versatility and privacy. If you are looking for an investment property, this turnkey home is set up to accommodate short-term, mid-term, and long-term rentals.Inside, you'll find a modern, well-maintained interior flooded with natural light, creating a welcoming atmosphere for relaxation and family gatherings. Situated in a family-friendly neighborhood with easy access to amenities and top-rated schools, this home is a rare find.Enjoy a cup of coffee and good conversation from the front porch or back deck. Whether you're seeking a family haven or a lucrative rental opportunity, this West Knoxville gem is ready to fulfill your desires. Located minutes away from Knoxville's top private schools. Schedule a tour today and call this fantastic property your own by Spring!
